      "- Dropdown (pick by city)\n",
      "\n",
      "Great first start:\n",
      "- Great for MVP\n",
      "- Fast\n",
      "- Less infrastructure\n",
      "\n",
      "Not ideal for user-facing search\n",
      "- Bad long term to use strings\n",
      "\n",
      "Conversion:\n",
      "- Database\n",
      "- Application layer (django, geo-django)\n",
      "- Front-end (javascript, encoding)\n",
      "\n",
      "Database:\n",
      "- Haversine formula in Mathematica (NO! too much math)\n",
      "- PostGIS, compute at DB level (NO! too much sql)\n",
      "- Spatical Database + Geo Django (YES!)\n",
      "\n",
      "Install PostgreSQL 9.2\n",
