      "- Distance between 2 points on a plane is not computationally intensive to calculate\n",
      "- Works for short distances very easily\n",
      "- Earth isn't flat, requires more work\n",
      "\n",
      "Modify models\n",
      "- geomodels\n",
      "- choose geography kwarg correctly\n",
